distances-siyam\/","url_meta":{"origin":31979,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Allah distances Hellfire from those who fast","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Amr ibn \u2018Abasah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts a day in the way of Allah, Allah will distance him from the Hellfire by a distance of one hundred years of travel.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 3249 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36284,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/22\/two-eyes\/","url_meta":{"origin":31979,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Weeping: Two eyes never touched by Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 22, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo eyes will never touch the Hellfire: an eye weeping from the fear of Allah, and an eye standing guard in the way of Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1639 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17151,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/12\/haya-jannah-badha-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":31979,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Modesty in Paradise, shamelessness in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty is part of faith and faith is in Paradise. Shamelessness is part of insolence and insolence is in Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2009 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14926,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/11\/daughters-shield-from-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":31979,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Children: His daughters are a shield from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever has three daughters and he is patient with them, he provides food and drink for them, and he clothes them, they will be his shield from the Hellfire on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/31979","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp